
List of features to complete before first release:

1.  Shapefiles
	Display shapefiles in radar view
	Allow customizable layers
	
2.  Radar Products
	Finish structures for radar products
	Allow rendering of all radar products
	Here are some additional classes needed:
		Renderer: render all radar products to a context given by RadarViewer or CLI (not in this version)
	
3.  Data sources
	Make gui for selecting and displaying various sources
	
4.  Web Access
	Allow for access to web for source data
	Here's the structure for this feature:
		FtpConnection - class to hold a single connection to a single server
		DataArchiver - class to hold multiple connections, time updates, and download updates
	
